This is the final release of my Glass_Climb map
Any problems or improvements suggest them please
Any one can put it on their server just dont change the name. Tell me if you
put it on your server as well.
_______________________________________________________________________
Changes in final release
added higher platform near the two back ladders from spawn.
Added teleporter in middle wall to the higher platform in stead of going
to the ladder.
_______________________________________________________________________
Changes in beta 2
Ladders are not spready all around the walls, only in corners and in middle
to get it the higher floor.
Blocks now gvie off glass gibs.
